items.name: Shannara Wiki - Exploring the Magical World of Shannara
items.title: Shannara Wiki - Exploring the Magical World of Shannara
items.headline: Be Enchanted by the magical world of Shannara at the Shannara Wikia
items.desc: The Shannara Wikia is a Wikia community created by fans of the Terry Brooks' Shannara series. This fantasy series includes the Word/Void trilogy, The Genesis of Shannara trilogy, the Legends of Shannara duology, as well as many other novels. In case you are interested in digging deep into the characters, novels, locations, and more that comprise this world - the Shannara Wikia community is definitely the place for you.

items.name: Hannah Montana Wiki
items.title: Hannah Montana Wiki
items.headline: Put your hands together for the Hannah Montana Wiki!
items.desc:
Hannah Montana Wiki is a collaborative encyclopaedia of information which covers everything to do with Disney Channel’s hit series about Miley Stewart's rock star life, starring Miley Cyrus.

We cover the music, episodes, cast, characters, and merchandise and just about everything else to do with the series.

items.name: Hanna-Barbera Wiki
items.title: Hanna-Barbera Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Hanna-Barbera Wiki
items.desc: Hanna-Barbera Wiki is a collaborative encyclopedia for everything related to William Hanna, Joseph Barbera and the Hanna-Barbera cartoon studio.  We cover everything from the Flintstones to Scooby-Doo to Yogi Bear. The wiki format allows anyone to create or edit any article, so we can all work together to create a comprehensive database for Hanna-Barbera fans.

items.name: Rihanna Wiki
items.title: Rihanna Wiki
items.headline: Learn more about Rihanna!
items.desc: The RiRipedia (The Rihanna Wikia) is a community site dedicated to Robyn Rihanna Fenty - aka "Rihanna". If you are a Rihanna fan, or if you're looking for more information about her, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and help us expand this database... or join us in discussion about her life, her career, or just Rihanna in general. All are welcome!
